| Context: To make the vanilla smoothie, first peel two ripe bananas and break them into chunks. Next, pour one cup of almond milk into the blender jar. Then, add a teaspoon of vanilla extract and a tablespoon of honey. After that, drop in three ice cubes to chill the mixture. Finally, blend on high speed for 45 seconds until smooth and pour into a glass. | Input: {"question": "List the actions in order."} | Output: {"answer": ["peel two ripe bananas and break them into chunks", "pour one cup of almond milk into the blender jar", "add a teaspoon of vanilla extract and a tablespoon of honey", "drop in three ice cubes to chill the mixture", "blend on high speed for 45 seconds until smooth and pour into a glass"]}

