| Context: To hang a picture frame, measure the desired height on the wall with a tape measure. Mark the spot lightly with a pencil where the nail should go. Hold the nail against the mark and hammer it in until only the head protrudes. Hook the wire on the back of the frame onto the nail head. Use a level to adjust the frame until it hangs perfectly straight. | Input: {"question": "List the actions in order."} | Output: {"answer": ["measure the desired height on the wall with a tape measure", "Mark the spot lightly with a pencil where the nail should go", "Hold the nail against the mark and hammer it in until only the head protrudes", "Hook the wire on the back of the frame onto the nail head", "Use a level to adjust the frame until it hangs perfectly straight"]}

| Context: The yoga session for beginners starts with sitting cross-legged on the mat. Take five deep breaths to center the mind and relax the shoulders. Move into the cat-cow stretch by arching and rounding the spine slowly. Hold the downward-facing dog pose for thirty seconds to stretch the hamstrings. End the practice by lying flat on the back in savasana for five minutes. | Input: {"question": "What steps were taken?"} | Output: {"answer": ["sitting cross-legged on the mat", "Take five deep breaths to center the mind and relax the shoulders", "Move into the cat-cow stretch by arching and rounding the spine slowly", "Hold the downward-facing dog pose for thirty seconds to stretch the hamstrings", "End the practice by lying flat on the back in savasana for five minutes"]}

| Context: Fixing the leaky faucet begins by shutting off the water supply valves under the sink. Remove the decorative cap on the handle and unscrew the retaining nut. Pull out the old washer and replace it with a new rubber one of the same size. Reassemble the handle and tighten the screw securely. Turn the water supply back on and check for any remaining drips. | Input: {"question": "List the actions in order."} | Output: {"answer": ["shutting off the water supply valves under the sink", "Remove the decorative cap on the handle and unscrew the retaining nut", "Pull out the old washer and replace it with a new rubber one of the same size", "Reassemble the handle and tighten the screw securely", "Turn the water supply back on and check for any remaining drips"]}

| Context: To build the birdhouse, cut the wooden planks to the specified dimensions using a saw. Drill a one-inch entrance hole in the front panel two inches from the top. Nail the side panels to the bottom board using galvanized nails. Attach the roof pieces at an angle to allow rain runoff. Paint the exterior with non-toxic sealant and hang it from a tree branch. | Input: {"question": "What steps were taken?"} | Output: {"answer": ["cut the wooden planks to the specified dimensions using a saw", "Drill a one-inch entrance hole in the front panel two inches from the top", "Nail the side panels to the bottom board using galvanized nails", "Attach the roof pieces at an angle to allow rain runoff", "Paint the exterior with non-toxic sealant and hang it from a tree branch"]}

