| Context: Performing a chemistry titration starts by rinsing the burette with the standard solution. Fill the burette to the zero mark and record the initial volume reading. Place the flask containing the unknown solution on the magnetic stirrer. Add the indicator drops and slowly release the titrant until the color changes permanently. Record the final volume and calculate the concentration difference. | Input: {"question": "What steps were taken?"} | Output: {"answer": ["rinsing the burette with the standard solution", "Fill the burette to the zero mark and record the initial volume reading", "Place the flask containing the unknown solution on the magnetic stirrer", "Add the indicator drops and slowly release the titrant until the color changes permanently", "Record the final volume and calculate the concentration difference"]}

