| Context: Preparing the pool for summer involves removing the winter cover and cleaning off debris. Vacuum the pool floor to eliminate settled dirt and leaves. Test the water chemistry using strips and adjust the pH levels accordingly. Shock the pool with chlorine tablets to kill any dormant bacteria. Turn on the filtration pump and let it run continuously for 48 hours. | Input: {"question": "What steps were taken?"} | Output: {"answer": ["removing the winter cover and cleaning off debris", "Vacuum the pool floor to eliminate settled dirt and leaves", "Test the water chemistry using strips and adjust the pH levels accordingly", "Shock the pool with chlorine tablets to kill any dormant bacteria", "Turn on the filtration pump and let it run continuously for 48 hours"]}

