| Context: To rotate the tires on the truck, lift the front end using a hydraulic jack and secure it with stands. Remove the front left tire and move it to the rear right position. Take the front right tire and install it on the rear left side. Shift the rear tires to the front positions in a straight cross pattern. Torque all lug nuts to the manufacturer specification and lower the vehicle. | Input: {"question": "What steps were taken?"} | Output: {"answer": ["lift the front end using a hydraulic jack and secure it with stands", "Remove the front left tire and move it to the rear right position", "Take the front right tire and install it on the rear left side", "Shift the rear tires to the front positions in a straight cross pattern", "Torque all lug nuts to the manufacturer specification and lower the vehicle"]}

